      <title>随着经济担忧加剧，土耳其股市进入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/turkish-stocks-flirt-with-bear-market-as-economic-concerns-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势的最新升级，土耳其股市进入熊市，因股票对当地投资者的吸引力下降以及对经济前景的担忧，市场原本就低迷的情绪进一步加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/turkish-stocks-flirt-with-bear-market-as-economic-concerns-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
